{"id":1667427,"retrievedAt":"2026-04-11T11:51:00.146Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[{"id":99,"name":"Documentary"}],"homepage":"https://franafutura.com/en/","id":1667427,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["IT"],"original_language":"it","original_title":"Frana Futura","overview":"Liguria is an impervious region, caught between the mountains and the sea. A network of deep valleys carved by streams flowing onto rocky coasts. Steep slopes collapse and wash out into the water. The Landslide has always permeated this territory; it is its natural geological - and ontological - conformation.  Those who live here tenaciously oppose the slipping away of the soil, working in a way that takes the form of care, but also of forcing the balance. Two forces that meet and shape each other: one pulling down, the other clinging and trying to resist.  Terracing after terracing, stone after stone, the landscape becomes an immense deposit of fatigue: human fatigue, animal fatigue, the fatigue of the roots that dig up the arid earth and break the walls, or hold them together; the fatigue of the stone, crushed between meanders and formations destined for infinite reshuffling.","popularity":0.0071,"poster_path":null,"production_companies":[],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"IT","name":"Italy"}],"release_date":"","revenue":0,"runtime":0,"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"No Language","iso_639_1":"xx","name":"No Language"}],"status":"Released","tagline":"Past - Present - Future","title":"Frana Futura","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","title":"Future Landslide","type":""}]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":6132018,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Luca Drovandi","original_name":"Luca Drovandi","popularity":0,"profile_path":null,"cast_id":22,"character":"Mason Crew","credit_id":"69d8e10ce5ebbe3adb5d2283","order":0}],"crew":[{"adult":fal